value:
Hi, $Nu! You
should try fighting in a swimsuit, too.$k$pIt'll keep you nice and cool, and it's
real easy to move around!

Before coming here, I fought a big
battle to win a trip to a tropical island.
And I won thanks to Arthur and Effie!

Anyone who works as hard as you
deserves a reward—so, here! I made
you a lei out of tropical flowers!

I think the whole Order of Heroes
should go for a great big swim
together!$k$pThough, I guess it would be bad if the
enemy attacked while we were all
at the beach...

I took a trip to a tropical island all by
myself. Doesn't that sound...mature?$k$pI'm inching closer to being a perfect
lady, aren't I? Well, aren't I?

I'm here with greetings just for you!
I was sent by
$Nf! Say...$k$pIs there somewhere around here I
can take a quick dip before I head
back?

Is this the summer Princess Elise
finally becomes a mature lady?!

Is this what my big sis meant by
"Summer helps a lady mature"?

Huh, what?! OK, I'll stop playing
and start concentrating. Promise!

This new power kinda makes me
want a new swimsuit to go with it.

I'm Princess Elise of Nohr! I was
playing on a tropical island, but...this
place looks pretty fun, too!

Tropical attaaaaack! Hyah!! Heehee,
did I scare you? Seeing you just got
me so excited!$k$pThat tropical island was a lot of fun,
but I've really come to love the
Askran Kingdom, too.$k$pEveryone in the Order of Heroes is
just so nice, and I get to play with so
many new people!$k$pBut... Well, can you keep a secret?$k$pI have the most fun playing with
you, $Nu!
I always look forward to your visits!$k$pHey, when we're all done fighting
someday, let's visit the beach
together.$k$pPinky swear! That makes it a promise!

Yay! This is fun!

Eheehee
My swimsuit is adorable!
Who wouldn't want to wear something like this on a beach?
How much do I love sunny beaches? Bunches and bunches!
Swimming sure makes a girl hungry!
Who needs tacky swimsuits to turn heads on a beach? I've got my bright smile!
I should get leis for my retainers. Red flowers for Arthur! White ones for Effie!
Oooh! Let's go lay on a beach after battle!
OK!
Ooh, hot!
Yay!
